# Placeholder: AST-grep rule directory for BDD step guards.
#
# Pre-commit hook entry: `ast-grep scan --rule .ast-grep/rules/`. ast-grep
# requires at least one rule file to scan a directory; this stub prevents
# the hook from failing with "Cannot read rule .ast-grep/rules/" on a fresh
# checkout. Real BDD-step structural guards will be added as .yml files
# alongside this placeholder.
